---
title: Blue Cheese Dauphinoise Pie with Leek and Green Beans
description: Our Blue Cheese Dauphinoise Pie is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/blue-cheese-dauphinoise-pie-4b6e492d-730cb6b1.jpg
